{"tid":681811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魯比奧指北韓不會放棄核計劃　讚特朗普做法令北韓難測","createTime":"2018-05-28T10:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T15:19:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5690ddd9e7881f9f1c4c30bdc9d2c72115e971bc","tid":681811,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"魯比奧指北韓不會放棄核計劃　讚特朗普做法令北韓難測<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1398476-20180528.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1398476-20180528.htm&d=Ss2A3sSqX1HWH8GxpL3HcMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d6fe158c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1398476-20180528.htm&h=b9fce11c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1398476-20180528.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨國會參議員魯比奧認定，北韓不會放棄核計劃。<br />\n<br />\n他接受美國廣播公司專訪時指，不相信北韓領袖金正恩會令朝鮮半島無核化，釋放美國公民和炸毀核試場地的舉動只是「做戲」，塑造自己開明和講道理的形象。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普日前去信北韓宣布取消美朝峰會，但不足24小時又改變口風，指不排除峰會可以如期在新加坡舉行。魯比奧讚揚特朗普的做法令北韓失去平衡，難以預計美方動向，又指這些無法觸摸的舉動，正正就是金正恩過往的行徑。"},{"pid":"ea63c718d0857b969fd47f9bcf7cc22ffcffb260","tid":681811,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c019e324224226865bc521e19ee160217dc23fe2","tid":681811,"uid":67043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"對付癲佬要癲過佢先得"},{"pid":"c2801d28f9b666f2344c65fec550a059b7715b80","tid":681811,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:30:54.000Z","msg":"魯比奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696aba9306e941133b6b7d7bdc0bcadc9271d1a8","tid":681811,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"希望佢2020選到"},{"pid":"89a7a80e65d23c4b3c4e0aa389aef95c490b8ffb","tid":681811,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}